{"tid":1668012,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"自從葉虎單野 中聯辦就變得好低調","createTime":"2019-10-21T18:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T05:18:18.000Z","uid":111585,"like":914,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"4940ba0e1e632469a3315193103f6f3c82465a02","tid":1668012,"uid":111585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:24:37.000Z","msg":"大家好似唔記得中聯辦先係港共政權既核心<br />\n咁多個月以黎再無人攻佢？"},{"pid":"66c17103bd063018e9b681552f1b9e521504f931","tid":1668012,"uid":68219,"like":621,"dislike":5,"score":616,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:39:40.000Z","msg":"你去港島攻俾我睇"},{"pid":"236b004eb7f3c1b118c6aa0a8243d1014b8dc19d","tid":1668012,"uid":59003,"like":333,"dislike":0,"score":333,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:44:12.000Z","msg":"有風吹去個邊就變西環特區<br />\n封撚左成個西環"},{"pid":"a774188395b1b9d77d0f9a32c7e9f69c397a04e7","tid":1668012,"uid":113000,"like":189,"dislike":0,"score":189,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:46:25.000Z","msg":"721土共黑警聯合策劃<br />\n<br />\n自始警隊信任度已為零<br />\n<br />\n多得佢唔少助攻<br />\n<br />\n已經等同六四級別每年都要集會"},{"pid":"273b415122b339bda210c23fcf777f1601567dc5","tid":1668012,"uid":268123,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:55:37.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"527999ebbe913977c08229139f5819c72d63048f","tid":1668012,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:56:23.000Z","msg":"師兄突破盲腸！唔講唔為意。"},{"pid":"e426b3b4f468c244bcba82eac444fde21524cb25","tid":1668012,"uid":107898,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"236b004eb7f3c1b118c6aa0a8243d1014b8dc19d","tid":1668012,"uid":59003,"like":333,"dislike":0,"score":333,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:44:12.000Z","msg":"有風吹去個邊就變西環特區<br />\n封撚左成個西環"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T19:16:45.000Z","msg":"一去港島<br />\n西環就重兵"},{"pid":"88393a99d268c8215ba428fa3ce6f2fe7b633773","tid":1668012,"uid":107898,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"a774188395b1b9d77d0f9a32c7e9f69c397a04e7","tid":1668012,"uid":113000,"like":189,"dislike":0,"score":189,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:46:25.000Z","msg":"721土共黑警聯合策劃<br />\n<br />\n自始警隊信任度已為零<br />\n<br />\n多得佢唔少助攻<br />\n<br />\n已經等同六四級別每年都要集會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T19:17:23.000Z","msg":"要糾纏721"},{"pid":"14f68fe8edc5cd4d3ac6dc5ba5c388c15d9ebcd4","tid":1668012,"uid":174607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T19:18:21.000Z","msg":"西環個次無咗幾多手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3b1b13732e17b81f2277d47aba08b151064fb6","tid":1668012,"uid":126151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T19:19:11.000Z","msg":"踢波比人紅牌掛"},{"pid":"dc23a49e664d091f9d2962fc3e6a1f2d0f21a9c6","tid":1668012,"uid":126151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd3b1b13732e17b81f2277d47aba08b151064fb6","tid":1668012,"uid":126151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T19:19:1